    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，横向布局。那支付环节如果超时怎么处理？工业场景下网络可能不稳定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PaymentProcessing",
        "PaymentTimeoutEvent",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "支付阶段设5分钟超时，重试策略用指数退避， telemetry流会监控这个过程。超时后触发PaymentTimeoutEvent，要同时取消支付和订单。另外支付失败本身也要走CancelOrder。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PaymentProcessing",
        "PaymentTimeoutEvent",
        "CancelPayment",
        "CancelOrder",
        "PaymentFailedEvent",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，支付节点和两条失败分支我加上了。那支付成功之后是进入库存预留对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PaymentProcessing",
        "StockReserving",
        "PaymentProcessedEvent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，StockReserving阶段。这里超时时间设2分钟，如果预留失败或者超时，都要退款并取消订单。我需要把补偿动作写清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "StockReserving",
